# warnings

## INEFFECTIVE_DYNAMIC_IMPORT

```text
[INEFFECTIVE_DYNAMIC_IMPORT] node4.js is dynamically imported by node3.js but also statically imported by node3.js, dynamic import will not move module into another chunk.

```

# Assets

## entry0.js

```js
//#region node0.js
globalThis.__acyclic_output_fuzz_0 = 0;
var node_0 = {};
node_0.value = 0;

//#endregion
export { node_0 };
```

## entry1.js

```js
import { node_3 } from "./entry3.js";
import { t as node2_exports } from "./entry2.js";

